Source: bash-libs
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: piseb <piseb@mailo.com>
Uploaders: Jean-Jacques Brucker <jjbrucker@foopgp.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), pandoc
Standards-Version: 4.5.1
Homepage: https://foopgp.org
Rules-Requires-Root: no
